responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "F8972DB845893C60209CC399B84E4BA2", "Is this some form of limerick! This is nothing more than a hunk of metal, not even fit as a weapon. I sense no essence flowing through this ancient weapon. The Scourge was a myth! I shall inform the Ensemble that our interests are at an end here. As for us, keep the scrap iron and maybe you can use it to buy my a drink at the Green Scarab sometime. Farewell.")
name: MIDD_0003_RRR_DaelaKav_20
